Interface ParsedTrack

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    InputModel

    public interface ParsedTrack
    Provides an immutable view of a MIDI track with efficient retrieval by time range.
    Author:
    Jay-R Studer

    • Method Detail

      • getNotePairs

        Iterable<EventPair<NoteEvent>> getNotePairs(long low,
                                            long high)
        Gets the note event pairs overlapping with the specified interval
        Parameters:
        low - the lower inclusive bound to return events for in microseconds
        high - the upper inclusive bound to return events for in microseconds
        Returns:
        a read only view of the portion of events overlapping the specified interval.
        Throws:
        IllegalArgumentException - if low is greater than high
